{"tid":2039714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解將一手資料pm人散出去","createTime":"2020-05-28T07:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T09:01:58.000Z","uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d031896867481dc161c92592ce5b449162956f","tid":2039714,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解有啲手足收到啲風，唔自己散出去<br />\n而係pm人叫人幫手散，我明大家都會緊張<br />\n大家都係為咗場運動好<br />\n但我真係唔太鍾意咁<br />\n<br />\n其實我寧願佢哋將啲資料自己散出去<br />\n好過搵我幫手散<br />\n雖然啲資料佢哋已fc,有啲甚至未fc都同我講<br />\n但內容太敏感，由我呢啲小薯講出嚟好易俾人當鬼<br />\n<br />\n我知你哋係唔會害我<br />\n但其實我唔太鍾意咩都交曬俾我散出去"},{"pid":"922b54fd1d5944a3ef552d3fa53c432024baa9c3","tid":2039714,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8e3e528111bc2b2f6d3f3013977cd0f715742a","tid":2039714,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T07:32:53.000Z","msg":"有種被利用嘅感覺<br />\n雖然大家講好齊上齊落<br />\n但我唔知自己咁樣算唔算太小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b33558187ad377e4144ab963fd1b71825605190","tid":2039714,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"922b54fd1d5944a3ef552d3fa53c432024baa9c3","tid":2039714,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"矮仔"},{"pid":"835493a2a442a77d0fd4de3e7ec62fe5dbdde029","tid":2039714,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b33558187ad377e4144ab963fd1b71825605190","tid":2039714,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"922b54fd1d5944a3ef552d3fa53c432024baa9c3","tid":2039714,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji